description: For sale: $400,000. Fabulous two-story located just blocks from Eastview HS.  Walk-in to the elevated foyer that will greet friends and family alike for years to come. Walk right out to your corner lot that is backed with a privacy fence and large cement patio! The upper level is framed with four bedrooms, a private master suite and organized closets!  The lower level is IDEAL for a guest bedroom or that teenager that needs a getaway.  Find the 5th bedroom and fourth bathroom in the Lower level while another gathering room, office, craft room, theater, exercise oasis awaits your finishing touches. Ideal location close to schools, highways, parks and trails! Welcome HOME!

Fantastic 4 bedroom, 4 bathroom custom home in a quiet neighborhood on a great lot! Enjoy entertaining guests in the large family room with wood burning fireplace just off of the kitchen. Walkout to the large deck and relax in the mostly fenced backyard. You will appreciate the convenience of 4 bedrooms on one level and the gorgeous recently updated upper level bath.  The huge master bedroom has a walk-in closet and 3/4 bath with gorgeous wooded views. The lower level walks out to the large backyard and has a 1/2 bath and plenty of space to add a 5th bedroom if you prefer. Minutes from the Mall of America, MN Zoo, Water park & Lebanon Hills Regional Park (2,000 acres), MSP Airport, and in the award winning 196 school district!
Coming soon: $330,000.

For sale: $450,000. So much to love about this impeccable two story just steps away from Eastview High School!  No neighbors behind you and West Facing gives you floods of sunlight from the east in the morning and sunsets out the front in the evening!  4 Generously sized Bedrooms on the upper level and a 5th Bedroom in the lower. Plenty of updates and custom touches throughout the home. A great value in an amazing and renowned neighborhood of Cedar Isle Estates!

description:
For rent: $1,795. Kari Anderson and REI Real Estate & Property Management are excited to present this fabulous townhome in Apple Valley. The unit is located on the end of the row, so there are less shared walls and a little extra room compared to the other units. The main floor consists of a huge living room, a nice-sized dining room that has a beautiful fireplace, a kitchen with a very open to feel to it, a balcony off of the kitchen, a coat closet and a small half bathroom. The lower level has a large family room, laundry area, storage closet and garage access. The upper level has a very large master bedroom with its own bathroom and walk-in closet, a hallway bathroom and two additional bedrooms. The master bathroom also has a jetted tub!

The home is located near off of 42 & Galaxie and is very close to tons of shopping options, parks, schools, transportation options and restaurants such as Osaka, Red Robin and El Azteca.

The tenant is responsible for gas and electric. Water, trash, sewer, lawn care and snow removal are taken care of by the association. Pets will be considered, but there are breed and weight restrictions. A pet deposit will be required. The home is available at any time!

description: Recently sold: $1,086,566. This beautiful 2 story, 3 bedroom, 3 bath home is ready for you to enjoy every season of the year. description: Recently sold: $453,000. An impressive two story home set on a private wooded lot, convenient to parks, shopping, downtown Minneapolis & St Paul and both airports. The home has had significant enhancements and a major addition in the recent past. The considerable living space on the main level (with newly refinished hardwood floors) makes it ideal for entertaining, with a spacious kitchen and dining area that opens to both a main floor family room (with gas fireplace) and an unparalleled amusement/game room (with built in bar, cabinetry, wine rack and shelving. The space extends to the outdoors with a multi-tiered deck, paver patio and screened gazebo which can be enjoyed by any sized gathering. A private office and a flex room (both with French glass doors) also on this level adding a component of privacy when the need arises. The home features four upper level bedrooms including a private master suite with full bath and walk in closet, a second bedroom with an en suite bathroom, and two additional bedrooms sharing a third full bathroom. This level also has a large laundry room with built in cabinetry, folding table and closet. The walkout lower level features an additional family room with a fireplace (ready for a gas insert) and a hidden, secured, wine closet. The game room addition (with separate furnace and air conditioning) has a 9 ½ foot ceiling and was originally designed for a golf simulator. Also on this level is a fifth bedroom with private bathroom, making it perfect for different living situations. The heated and insulated garage features an epoxy floor and has an attached workshop that is second to none. The home must be experienced to be appreciated.

Recently sold: $279,900. Beautiful Townhome  in the heart of Apple Valley! Unit features many amenities and upgrades. Large kitchen with granite, stainless, and ceramic floor.  Open living room with fireplace and built-in shelving.  Optional dining/ office. Powder room and nice laundry area with cabinetry completes the main level.  Upper level features hardwood floors throughout.  Large master bedroom with master bath with separate shower, whirlpool, and walk-in closet . 2nd bedroom with full bath.  Nice optional area for office/den or overnight guests.

description:
For rent: $2,950. 4 bedroom 4 bath *end unit* luxury town home. 4 story, 3 years old. Private row house community. Two car tuck-under garage, first floor spacious entry and flex room with French doors. Second floor kitchen gleaming with granite counters, SS appliances, 5 burner gas range, wall mount oven and convection microwave, plus and walk-in pantry. Beautifully updated with light throughout. Living room, dining and kitchen all on the second level. Peaceful master suite with private bath and custom closet. Convenient same level laundry, 2 more bedrooms, and full bath all on the 3rd floor. The fourth floor includes an additional master bedroom with 2 closets and full bath, but could also serve as an additional living space, studio, office, or guest area. Enjoy nearby East Park, miles of paved trails, 36 acre lake with fishing dock, several playgrounds, and a community pool! Shopping and restaurants all nearby. Less than 30 minutes to downtown Twin Cities, airport, MN Zoo, and Mall of America. Acclaimed #196 school district.
Call today to arrange a private showing.
HOA requires 12 month lease. Part of the Trey Point neighborhood, within Cobblestone Lake.
Privately managed by on-site property manager.

Owner pays association (trash/recycling, snow removal) and water. Tenant pays electric, gas, TV/internet/phone.
Recently sold: $300,000.

description: Recently sold: $304,000. One owner well cared for throughout the years in the sought after Hunter Wood's neighborhood. 3 car garage! Nicely landscaped on a beautiful wooded 1/2 lot, brick pavers, patio, deck area. Well constructed home, hardy board siding, vaulted ceilings, 2 beautiful brick fireplaces with full brick to the ceiling & raised hearth. 3 season porch, separate formal dining area. Nice big kitchen with updated appliance, Bosch dishwasher, built in desk, ceramic tile. Nice sized master suite with walk in closet, pocket door, make up area, and 3/4 bathroom. Full guest bathroom & another bedroom upstairs. Lower level walkout family room with a fireplace, good sized laundry room with nice built ins for extra storage spaces. 2 additional bedroom and a lower 3/4 bathroom. Updated furnace, water heater, driveway, new carpeting.

Recently sold: $250,000. Well updated and maintained twin home with no association fee! Perfect location with easy access to MN Zoo, freeways, downtowns, airport, shopping and dining. New roof, steel siding, manicured grounds and a pond view. Fresh, neutral dcor with open flowing floorplan sought after by todays buyer. Gleaming white enamel cabinetry kitchen and appliances with window overlooks front yard and entry. The dinette is open to both the kitchen and main living room and boasts hardwood flooring. Pop the popcorn and curl up in the living room for movie night. Nature is just outside the patio door, relaxing pond views with plentiful bird sightings. There is still time to gather here for a quick dinner! Two bedrooms with full bath walk through and ample closet space. The lower level walkout offers a large game room with fireplace, plus a secondary gathering area and two more bedrooms with updated 3/4 bath.  New furnace and A/C, electric panel being installed.
Recently sold: $295,000.

description:
Recently sold: $190,500. This town home is a quad style so you have minimal shared walls. The main level features vaulted ceilings with an open floor plan for the kitchen, dining, and living room. The private, no maintenance deck is right off the dining room for easy entertaining. Two bedrooms and a full bathroom complete the upstairs. The large master bedroom features an over-sized walk in closet and laundry shoot. The lower level boasts a large living room with walk out to cement patio and small, private yard. A third bedroom, 3/4 bath, laundry room, and garage access complete this fully renovated home. Garage is a generous two car size and includes built in storage. Rent price includes garbage service, snow removal, and lawn mowing. Tenant responsible for gas, electric, water, cable/internet/phone. Perfect location with easy access to stores, yet in a quiet neighborhood. 1 mile away from Hyvee & Target on Pilot Knob and 1 mile away from Home Depot, Sam's Club, and Menards.

Pricing based on 1 year lease. Longer lease agreement may result in discounted monthly rent price. Price includes garbage/recycling, snow removal, and lawn care. Other utilities are in addition to the monthly rent price. Friendly dog allowed, no cats, no smoking.

description: Recently sold: $269,000. Original owner, well-kept stately two story colonial home nestled on a lush green and very private Cul-de-sac setting with a mature landscape.  The private fenced in back yard features a vast, ground level deck  adjoining the paver stone patio and water feature gardens.  The main level features freshly refinished original Oak hardwood flooring throughout the open living room and adjoining dining room.  The kitchen features ample storage with Oak raised panel custom cabinetry.  Separate cooktop with built in oven and microwave.  The convenient main floor half bath features beautiful Venetian plastered walls, marble floors and a freestanding vessel sink.  Upstairs you will discover three freshly painted bedrooms with gleaming refinished original hardwood oak flooring and a full bath featuring mosaic ceramic tiled floor and updated vessel vanity with a marble top.  The basement level has a 11x17 rec room with plenty of additional storage space and good upgraded sound mechanicals.

Upper level includes Master Suite with a walk-through full bath, 2nd bedroom and 2nd floor laundry! Enjoy your 10x8 patio space in this great location with access to many amenities and shops!

Recently sold: $270,000. Wow! You will love this incredibly convenient area of Apple Valley and this gorgeous fenced lot on a culdesac. Walk to nearby Metro Transit Station and Galaxie Park. Enjoy updated windows, mechanicals and appliances. Features white oak hardwood throughout the main floor, 3 bedrooms on one level, 2 non conforming bedrooms/flex rooms in basement, ample storage, additional parking pad, shed with playhouse, fresh paint, newer lower level carpet and so much more.

Recently sold: $349,000. Relax or entertain in all seasons ~ fun with Two-Tier large Deck complete with deluxe Hot Tub!! Private Vaulted Owners Suite offering Skylights, Fireplace, Walk-in closet, Heated Floor Tiles, Jetted tub, separate Tiled Shower. Romantic, Spa styled Suite walks out to Deck and Hot Tub for Treetop west facing sunset views! Great Room style-Open Kitchen/Dining/Living. 3/4 Cotter Grade Oak Hdwd flrs, Corian Island, LG appliances and Skylight.One Main Level Bedroom walks through to full Main Bath. Terrific for entertaining inside and out! Spacious Dining area walks out to Party-sized Deck! Lower level Family room, Workout area and huge 4th bedroom! 3/4 bath adjoins Bedroom and Family Room. Cement driveway, attached 2 car garage, shop nook and walk through storage. Excellent location with great walkability to  Caribou, restaurants, shopping, banks, theater,Target  and music! Near Park n Ride and Bus access. A uniquely styled and updated home on flat, usable fenced yard. Enjoy life here!

Recently sold: $660,000. This magnificent custom home is located on a quiet, 1/4-acre corner lot in the picturesque, master-planned community of Cobblestone Lake. One of Cobblestone's original "jewel box" houses -- designed by architect Ron Brenner and brought to life by builder Kyle Hunt & Partners -- the timeless design offers both elegance and superb functionality. No detail has been overlooked. Top-quality features include 5" character-grade hardwood floors throughout most of the home; meticulously-maintained enameled millwork and cabinetry; stunning windows flooded with natural light; open floor plan offering true vintage style; custom tile in kitchen, living and baths; walnut counters, rails and built-ins; 3 bedrooms up with large bonus room (easily converted to a bedroom, if desired); and a spacious 2+ car garage. The professionally installed and maintained landscape by award-winning Biota includes several special flowering trees, shrubs, and perennials plus a fabulous stone patio. The daylight lower level features an additional 900 +/- SF for future finishing. Don't miss this once in a lifetime opportunity! A true 10+!  Buyer's agents are welcome.

description:
For rent: $2,750. Lovely 3 bedroom 2.5 bath *end unit* luxury town home with open concept, row house style, 3 story modern layout.
Great entertaining space and kitchen with gorgeous flooring and natural light with a stunning southwest view of Cobblestone Lake from the living room.
Quartz counters, SS appliances, walk-in pantry, and a full deck off kitchen. Luxurious master suite with private bath and custom closet, 2 add'l bedrooms, full bath and laundry all on the upper level. A tuck-under 3 car garage with a ton of storage makes this place easy to settle into. Stress free living, no yard work or shoveling, plenty of great views and outdoor space to enjoy as well. Pet-friendly.

Trey Point is part of the Cobblestone Lake community:
Miles of paved trails, 36 acre lake with fishing dock, several playgrounds, and a community pool! Shopping and restaurants all conveniently nearby. Less than 30 minutes to downtown Twin Cities, airport, MN Zoo, and Mall of America. Acclaimed #196 school district.
Call Jennifer today to arrange your private showing.Privately managed by on-site property manager.
HOA fees and water *included* in the rent. $2750/month

12 month lease. Association dues (includes snow removal, trash/recycling, lawn care, pool/amenities) and water for the unit all *included* in the rent price. Tenant pays only gas and electric, TV/Internet.

description:
Recently sold: $329,500. Johnny Cake Rd is closed but this gem is open for sale! Details here will impress! Amazing turn-key walkout with 5 BR(3 on one level), 2 baths, 2 car
garage and the perfect 2nd kitchen on lower level-compact, functional,
better than a wet bar! Gorgeous remodel of the main level kitchen and bathroom,
the detail work of this home was not overlooked. Custom-designed kitchen has beautiful cabinets, quartz counters, tile backsplash, stainless steel
appliances and farmhouse sink, even instant boiling water. New flooring throughout most of the main level and foyer/stairs - kitchen and
living room open and spacious! The new main bath remodel is a WOW! Lower
level walkout calls for fun and entertaining with a wood burning fireplace &
full kitchen and bar/counter area for movies, BBQs and guests. Current
owners replaced all windows, front door and glass slider, roof and gutters,
furnace, AC, water heater, and hired blown insulation for energy savings. Located on a quiet street with fenced and shaded backyard.

Recently sold: $420,000. This Stunning 2 story features a gourmet kitchen featuring extensive counter space,a down draft Jenner range, butlers pantry /buffet bar plus informal and formal dining , The dining room could be an office, there are hardwood floors and new carpets throughout the home , a huge master suite with walk in closet, vaulted ceiling, spa bath & more plus 3 more bedrooms upstairs.The upper level main bath has double sinks and a separate bathing area and commode. The lower level boasts a bar, fireplace, game area plus an exercise room. This home has been thoroughly gone through by Cocoon for high efficiency energy performance.  The over sized 3 1/2 garage is sheet rocked and has an epoxy floor finish extra high ceilings,shelving and a service door leasing to the back yard. The back yard has a stamped concrete patio that is enclosed by a privacy hedge just off the kitchen.There are sun filled raised bed gardens  and a swing set for fun. Move in ready home for your convenience.  Eastview HS area

For sale: $375,000. Stay home & safely tour w/a Virtual Open House Sunday 4/5/20 12-12:30. Download and register the Zoom app on your phone or computer. Copy & Paste https://zoom.us/meeting/register/tZwqd-qpqD8j3Gsvzvw3Vm4Dg1mbvFhaIw 

Fantastic 4 bedroom, 4 bathroom custom home in a quiet neighborhood on a great lot! Enjoy entertaining guests in the large family room with wood burning fireplace just off of the kitchen. Walkout to the large deck and relax in the mostly fenced backyard. You will appreciate the convenience of 4 bedrooms on one level and the gorgeous recently updated upper level bath.  The huge master bedroom has a walk-in closet and 3/4 bath with gorgeous wooded views. The lower level walks out to the large backyard and has a 1/2 bath and plenty of space to add a 5th bedroom if you prefer. Minutes from the Mall of America, MN Zoo, Water park & Lebanon Hills Regional Park (2,000 acres), MSP Airport, and in the award winning 196 school district!

description:
Recently sold: $232,000. Welcome Home! Beautiful, modern and spacious Town home in excellent and upscale Apple Valley neighborhood and school district 196. No Section 8 at this time.
This town home features:
1. 3 Bedrooms and 2 baths on one level.
2. Open floor plan, and vaulted ceilings.
3. Cozy gas burning fireplace in the warm living room.
4. Open kitchen with island seating and plenty of storage.
5. Spacious master bedroom with a private master bathroom with double vanity and a large walk in closet. There are also 2 nice sized bedrooms with a common bathroom.
6. Separate Washer and dryer room all on the same floor.
7. Formal dining area perfect for entertaining. Can be used as an office instead.
8. Gated community pool.
9. Attached 2 car garage giving you 4 parking spaces. There are also common parking areas directly across for additional visitors.
10. Enjoy Spring, Summer and Fall on your personal deck dotted with trees.
11. Your home is located within a short walk to shops, restaurants, LA fitness center etc.
12. Few minutes drive to the highway(Cedar/77) and the Apple Valley transit station and all shopping.

Utilities included are Trash, Water, Sewer, Lawn care, and Snow removal. Renter responsible for Gas and Electric

Recently sold: $305,000. Charming updated 4 bed, 2 bath home on expansive .66 acre private and fenced lot. Large inviting kitchen with center island, granite countertop & stainless steel appliances. Living room complete with hardwood floors. Spacious deck over looks incredible backyard. Brand new windows on main floor and patio doors up and down. Theater room in garage, finished w/o basement with wood burning fireplace. Fantastic location close to schools and the MN Zoo.

Recently sold: $406,000. Get away from it all with your own backyard oasis! This 4 bedroom home is ideally situated on a cul-de-sac lot.  Expansive main level offers both formal and informal living areas.  The home office is well positioned on the main floor for privacy and overlooks the in-ground swimming pool. Updated gourmet kitchen features double ovens, granite countertops, distinctive tile backsplash and more!  4 season sunroom is the ideal place for relaxation!  3 bedrooms on one level featuring an upper level Master Suite with a gorgeous spa-inspired bathroom with jetted tub, tiled shower and an abundance of natural light.  
Room to entertain in the lower level with an amusement room, family room, 4th   bedroom, bathroom and storage! 
Truly a unique opportunity to own a piece of paradise in Apple Valley!
